  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something  is putting the frogs of Ribbit Island in danger, and it is up to you to save them! Traverse the island to find and slay \"The Lost Legend\"! What is that anyway?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield the Red Seraphine Lily on your head and get ready to fight \"The Lost Legend\" in this short RPG with only ONE battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the truth of the frogs' past and explore the world of NO HAPPY DAYS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Features:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Only one fight! ... \"The Lost Legend\"! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Friendly frogs ready to make you smile! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Art and Original Music full of life and personality </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A... secret?? Wait... who did that \"frog\" see in the maze?  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > . . . </p></li></ul>",
